      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 4,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      543.94,
      526.19,
      556.98
    ],
    "text": "The Trial Judge who has the sole discretion in imposing a sentence which is",
