    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      185.69,
      526.3,
      198.73
    ],
    "text": "sentence is a matter of discretion and it is well settled that when discretion",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 5,
    "bbox": [
      144.02,
      212.21,
      526.32,
      225.25
    ],
    "text": "has been properly exercised along accepted judicial lines, an appellate court",
    "fonts": [
      "Century"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
